{"tid":2393582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國夥日本成立「通訊安全基金」 抗衡中國5G攻勢","createTime":"2021-02-03T14:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T07:22:09.000Z","uid":134071,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4a0c30a1af101eef84188e663cf3adb7029201","tid":2393582,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2466956673455651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fposts%2F2466956673455651&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c11a53c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2466956673455651</a><br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰 Nathan Law<br />\n <br />\n9 小時  &middot;<br />\n【🇺🇸美國戰線｜日媒：五眼將夥日本成立「通訊安全基金」 抗衡中國5G攻勢 重掌資安主導權】<br />\n<br />\n為了抗𧗽中共5G攻勢及所衍生的國安問題，日本《讀賣新聞》引述消息表示，<strong>美國將成立「跨國通訊安全基金」 ，成員除了五眼聯盟外，亦會罕有地包括日本，形成新的「對中聯盟」，協助各國重掌5G主導權。</strong><br />\n<br />\n基金將用作強化六國5G技術開發、加強供應網絡、鼓勵使用可靠製造商，而相關基金的創立已經包含在美國國會上月初通過的《國防授權法》撥款當中。現時基金所需總金額仍未決定，但國會曾表示約為五億美元，為期十年。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，美國為了抗衡中共，須靠技術較強的日本幫忙，加上汽車、醫療、電力等各方面都要涉及5G技術，若依賴中共技術則很可能被間諜及駭客入侵，故各國已致力開拓供應網。<br />\n<br />\n查實美日兩國去年已同意共同開拓5G供應鏈，英日政府11月亦宣布合作興建5G通訊網。現時未知「安全基金」成立後，會否邀請更多國家及組織，如歐盟、台灣加入；但即使以現時規模，相信足以在供應鏈層面回應中國攻勢，並在盟友之間建立優勢，對抗中共。"},{"pid":"1a10edec8d1fb6e3de60663a0ba85526cc5db736","tid":2393582,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Yomiuri_Online/status/1355972885509251079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYomiuri_Online%2Fstatus%2F1355972885509251079&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=e69baaba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYomiuri_Online%2Fstatus%2F1355972885509251079&h=22e009aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Yomiuri_Online/status/1355972885509251079</a>"},{"pid":"11efacae985dd2f7f1e7f4c0c919c02eda4966be","tid":2393582,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8709a2ec48889657f0daa0c80c38f4cd82fc2ea","tid":2393582,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"一早應該啦"},{"pid":"de384036a7b3760c3e2c2bee3a450e5aa3e85237","tid":2393582,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8709a2ec48889657f0daa0c80c38f4cd82fc2ea","tid":2393582,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"一早應該啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee06d8f686ab99e8b6e6e9f1e878c9c65bcacba6","tid":2393582,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"連登分化五毛：拜登上台就唔會對付支那啦"},{"pid":"121a47b30f54698c00d577aea867bd550d0ea226","tid":2393582,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f835dacd901b1f6eccebfcb233d2b7f820054c81","tid":2393582,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121a47b30f54698c00d577aea867bd550d0ea226","tid":2393582,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse